{"tid":1470630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"贏，一齊贏；輸，你哋輸","createTime":"2019-08-14T06:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T07:28:17.000Z","uid":143547,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bde2e46842550876a043b6f42cb6883be907a133","tid":1470630,"uid":143547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:05:18.000Z","msg":"又話<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n齊上齊落<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不分化<br />\n不割蓆</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌完未呀<br />\n贏咗觀感， 咁你爭取到訴求未呀？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> <span style=\"color: red;\">贏要一齊贏呀</span> </span>"},{"pid":"a2d9a621437f105f41d351397b61866b32baec91","tid":1470630,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:06:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勁勁推</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"26b78185b9249b5d92db5a4acd991c9ae7806974","tid":1470630,"uid":143547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:10:15.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"f907321dad49841c0abf461bdb1609254506a0d0","tid":1470630,"uid":143547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:18:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79aaabd8bb5336ab3a9117ce0f747036184075d4","tid":1470630,"uid":143547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:19:25.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<br />\n唔好畀分化狗得逞<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"ede89faee6eedad04228911be794d99dd4661ca2","tid":1470630,"uid":143547,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:35:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">批評很容易<br />\n但唔該將心比己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要人夠多，咁先有力量。<br />\n勇武又好，和你非又好。<br />\n<br />\n個個都做 free Rider， 仲鬧走埋做嘢嘅人， <br />\n咁就真係玩完</span></span>"},{"pid":"df0a5013e3e04f49dd9faaf40b8c450a74558083","tid":1470630,"uid":265305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bde2e46842550876a043b6f42cb6883be907a133","tid":1470630,"uid":143547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:05:18.000Z","msg":"又話<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n齊上齊落<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不分化<br />\n不割蓆</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌完未呀<br />\n贏咗觀感， 咁你爭取到訴求未呀？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> <span style=\"color: red;\">贏要一齊贏呀</span> </span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:37:25.000Z","msg":"yeah 清晰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UQFM4nS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUQFM4nS.gif&h=a74ab43d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UQFM4nS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUQFM4nS.gif&h=a74ab43d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UQFM4nS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUQFM4nS.gif&h=a74ab43d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知道指責前線既人咩諗法定係一毛，解釋一次：<br />\n係政府（共黨)<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>A行為</strong></span>只會煲大對自己有利既point ， <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">B行為</span></strong>冷處理所有已fc做錯既事（狗濫權），<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">C行為</span></strong>無中生有屈對方 (收錢遊行)<br />\n對方係政權(港共+狗)，香港人係冇權冇槍既市民。<br />\n孫中山人數上由壓倒毛澤東到落敗到台灣，係衰左係政治上唔夠老毛賤格，做唔出BC行為。 <br />\n示威者人數由200萬到而加有大量因爲爆玻璃行為搖擺不定而減到唔知得返幾多。<br />\n要贏到共黨政權得一樣方法 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">B</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">C</span>行為</strong>做得誇過對方。<br />\n盲撐可能用錯字，我用攬字。<br />\n攬等於= <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span> +<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">B</span></strong><br />\n你話道徳淪喪既？ 我明白。但請唔好係打仗時期對外大宣稱自己友做錯呀喪屌呀。想屌咪整連儂牆囉。 <br />\n連登都幾多淺黃中立入黎睇，唔好做衰示威者團結形象啦。<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><ins>欣賞冇被狗搞到憤怒蒙蔽自己既大家</ins></span>，亦希望大家明白政權歷史到現在既手段一樣污穢不堪，我地冇殺人冇姦淫冇大屠殺，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">用返抹黑老作還擊對方時，你可以做唔出，但請放下政治潔癖，冷處理自己友做得唔好既地方，擁護自己友直至打低強權。</span></strong></span><br />\n最後，五毛三毛一毛死三代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf980793b831c7dbb1453b7450b1a5c820c99f17","tid":1470630,"uid":143547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:38:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不割蓆<br />\n不譴責<br />\n齊上齊落<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"73e3ae2cb9d7affaffa658674eb9121ded80e02a","tid":1470630,"uid":143547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6db65f3cd20e875ed64aa8d1e560f9c3c9948bee","tid":1470630,"uid":245371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:41:33.000Z","msg":"[思想改革] 抗爭者的思路<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470637</a>"},{"pid":"baf8b49cfdbdcd607ed1ba765ac53ba5b836beb3","tid":1470630,"uid":143547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:49:34.000Z","msg":"推！！！"},{"pid":"18b3e0423a61bebc92ed671bb9f180bacb2cdd02","tid":1470630,"uid":143547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c14e2c183e4eff62126305c24b23bc4d679991a","tid":1470630,"uid":261530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:50:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3566beb1a5c0d0c646484561c96f72bbf37792b","tid":1470630,"uid":947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0